    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents on the passenger side, and early signs of rust on the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission hesitates during shifts; it likely needs a comprehensive overhaul. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This is an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the right tools and time.",
      "price": 6500.0,
