    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with all major systems currently in good working order. While the exterior looks great from a distance, there are a few minor door dings and some light scratches consistent with its age. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though there is some slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
